Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:34.73,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\i0\an1\fad(150,150)}Hey(/≥▽≤/)!Hey!(/≥▽≤/){\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:38.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}飽きるくらい　全部キミがほしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:40.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ハートは涙でいっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:45.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}恋のいろはとかまだわかってないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何度も繰り返すけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:51.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}寸前でまた次回へ　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:57.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}スイートな乙女心は　あいにく取り扱ってないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ねぇ　これがI LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:04.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Someday I really really send it, precious for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:09.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Someday I really really send it, precious for you!
